description: The total token supply of Xenia coins will be capped at 200 million tokens. Out of this 25 percent of the tokens will be allocated during the main ICO. An additional 10 percent is set aside for the cost of the ICO, 7.5 will be used to support the project while the remaining 67.5 percent will be reserved in escrow. The main aim of the ICO is to raise funds for the raiding of assets, 90% of the platform development has been initialized by the founder.
name: Xenia Coin
